--- xochitla2006 <xochitla2006@...> wrote:

> Unciron:
> 
> "Try to find out the extention of damage that the traitor cause" 
> hissed the Unicron "We should also reformate our segurity system in 
> order THIS wont happen again"

Vorpal chuckled darkly, "The security systems have been repaired." He
glanced at Unicron, "I do not have the full logs, but i do believe she
used a plasma burst to hide her escape?"

Vorpal shook his head as he continued, "But I have been examining the
last scans of one of the previous attacks on Atlantis before Cyclonus
arrived. The scans of one of our lost soldiers - Injustice. The last
scans went off the charts!" Another dark chuckle from Vorpal as he
continued, "I believe we have a way now to recreate that, and more.
Perhaps a new weapon we can use against the Cybertronians!"

Cyclonus looked over at Vorpral but said nothing, holding his council
for the moment. 

Scourge on the other hand frowned. Scourge KNEW there was no one better
than he and his sweeps for handling anything on that mudball of a
planet. But like Cyclonus he held his silence, but it was difficult. 

Preston
(Da'minion)
